data.description: Due to a family emergency no showings till December 7th. This property is situated on about a 1/2 acre Boasting a 2-car detached Pole barn/Garage, and a 2 1/2-car attached garage. This spacious home includes in-law facilities with a separate entrance, Central a/c, and a Bathroom with—a Jacuzzi tub and shower. The spacious Kitchen/Dining room area overlooks the fenced-in yard, where an above-ground pool makes for relaxing summer days. A tankless hot water system is included.
